name: mugniul/tune-enhancer
description: Elevate your audio experience with TuneEnhancer. This plugin allows you to select two different audio tracks from your media library-one for standard playback and the other for enhanced audio. Seamlessly switch between tracks with a customizable \"Enhance Audio\" button, perfect for showcasing before-and-after audio effects. Fully integrated with WordPress, TuneEnhancer makes it easy to create engaging audio experiences on your website.
